Please provide the following information in the [Automatic Dependency Management with Maven 2|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/BAMBOO/Setting+up+Build+Dependencies;jsessionid=697887C2DDD4C80CE232B06AFA47EE63#SettingupBuildDependencies-AutomaticDependencyManagementwithMaven2]:

{quote}
Bamboo only do dependency management for SNAPSHOT dependencies for example:
{code}
 <dependency>
    <groupId>DenpendciesTestParent</groupId>
    <artifactId>DenpendciesTestParent</artifactId>
    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
  </dependency>
 </dependencies>
</project>
{code}
{quote}
